Descripition
-------------

/core/ 		- contains generic classes (accessable only for apache user)
/cli/ 		- contains cron jobs and cron helpers (accessable only for apache user) 
/protected 	- contains application's files (accessable only for apache user)
/web/ 		- document root, should be accessable from world wide. 
/db/		- contains DB table\data to import (should not be uploaded to production) 
-------------


How to use 
-------------

1. Import /db/ files to ur database
2. Edit /protected/configs/app.php and all other related files
3. run $>php cli/get_currencies.php 
4. hit http://localhost/index.php
5. insert currencies and hit the button 
-------------

Nice to have 
-------------
Memcache is supported automatically if installed.
